Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.80,0:01:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.90,0:01:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒支配這座山的\N邪惡帝皇多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.47,0:01:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一邊在各界層\N與多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.40,0:01:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊向第七界層前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.74,0:01:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了令在第四界層\N變成了龍之王的龍神丸復活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上到第五界層的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.55,0:01:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追著蝴蝶到西裏露森林\N去找復活聖水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.43,0:02:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十二話\N必看!龍王丸誕生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.51,0:02:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.28,0:02:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虎王大人不見了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.69,0:02:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是悄悄地偷走了出去\N東哥羅那傢伙很不知所措呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.33,0:02:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這便好了\N萬一虎王大人出了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東哥羅也不會沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.20,0:02:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後只要把渡幹掉\N便解決一切了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.64,0:02:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達大人的親衛我們獨佔\N東哥羅沒有資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.02,0:03:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你饒恕我,污煙大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.99,0:03:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真蠢材\N把渡追趕至此竟也失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.49,0:03:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎?沒有第三次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘兄弟不會容忍你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.30,0:03:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次我一定會\N打倒渡他們給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.64,0:03:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要這樣啊\N也是為了你的性命著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.54,0:03:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛布力奇2號去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.59,0:03:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那蝴蝶從剛才起便不動了\N為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.60,0:03:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道不會就這樣死去了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,不要說奇怪的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.20,0:03:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也要喚醒龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.17,0:03:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後打倒多惡達\N這也是為了村中的各人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村中的各人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的村啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.21,0:04:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達把村內的人都施了咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.10,0:04:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此,我也變成了這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.08,0:04:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背叛了多惡達\N我便不能恢復原來的樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.78,0:04:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在我覺得\N怎樣也沒所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.32,0:04:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是…多惡達所做的事\N不能饒恕,絕對不能饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也在想\N你成為了多惡達的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定有什麼原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.06,0:04:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生以前是什麼樣子的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是非常有型的男子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有型嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.81,0:05:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.45,0:05:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙霧在飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蝴蝶飛了進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要進去裏面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進去!進去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這便是西裏露森林嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.82,0:05:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有花啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.45,0:05:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,你真努力\N好,接著只剩下復活聖水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這裏是否真是西裏露森林?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,復活聖水到底在哪裏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來分頭找比較好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.81,0:06:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚇一跳嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子\N現在不是玩的時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我非常喜歡這裏\N一直留在此吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是老虎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.86,0:06:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!\N我會用野牛武一郎流斬你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.30,0:06:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們啊,經常也是這樣做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.47,0:06:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有難的時候\N不是要互相幫助嗎?拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.17,0:06:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?火美子不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.54,0:06:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵捉賊啊!兵捉賊啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來捉我吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.00,0:07:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼欺負老虎先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是玩不成兵捉賊了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵捉賊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.68,0:07:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我來和你玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.91,0:07:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來捉兵,你快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.82,0:07:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,兵大哥,來捉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.29,0:07:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉到你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軟弱的傢伙,真無聊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.80,0:08:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次到我做兵了\N我來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉到你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.50,0:08:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡你\N女人要強才是最好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.90,0:08:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做我的新娘吧\N你真幸運呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼新娘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.71,0:08:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是替我做飯、幫我穿鞋等等\N很高興吧,喜歡吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新娘、新娘!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.75,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可愛的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.85,0:08:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!火美子!火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,你沒事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不懂問人的禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫虎王,你又是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.20,0:08:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是又有趣又有型\N世人的英雄,戰部渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.17,0:08:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.88,0:09:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡?我好像在哪裏聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,走了,火美子\N大家很擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.42,0:09:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟碰我的新娘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.75,0:09:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新娘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.49,0:09:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是新娘、新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東哥羅那混蛋\N竟找到來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.01,0:09:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!停一停,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.20,0:09:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日就此放你一馬\N下次再碰我的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會就此算數的\N知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.09,0:09:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!渡!火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.49,0:09:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅!在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,在這裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子也沒事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是新娘、新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新娘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟把我的班京…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.41,0:10:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我們幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.78,0:10:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收聲!這個森林\N是第五界層最後的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不會交給多惡達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.75,0:10:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啊\N我們是為了和多惡達作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.75,0:10:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而來找復活聖水的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.52,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你們會知道\N復活聖水的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是胡娜拉像告訴我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡娜拉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.13,0:10:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說你們\N聽到胡娜拉的聲音嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.08,0:10:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看,這些花便是一百年\N才開一次的西裏路花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.42,0:10:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想要的是復活聖水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.16,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些花開的時候所流出的水\N便是復活聖水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.40,0:11:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.50,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次西裏路花開的時候\N已是一百年以上的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.10,0:11:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來是早已開花了\N可是照現在這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些花蕾不會打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.71,0:11:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.48,0:11:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那些污煙的關係\N要花蕾開花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.98,0:11:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便需要有直接的陽光照射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.42,0:11:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.79,0:11:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼辛苦才來到這裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打起精神吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.72,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要令陽光照射到這些花便行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用空神丸旋轉衝上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令雲層開一個洞嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.34,0:11:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,空神丸\N給我看看你的力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.15,0:11:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!空神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.84,0:12:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背叛者古拿瑪\N找到你了,去死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.64,0:12:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希度羅拿\N現在沒有時間陪你,走開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃得掉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.69,0:13:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於找到你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.63,0:13:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙何時來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陽光照不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.53,0:13:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣西裏路花不會開花的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.97,0:13:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧,這群嘍囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,你還未受夠嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以讓你阻礙我的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.54,0:13:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這打不倒我希度羅拿大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招,高熱火炎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.75,0:13:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我在這裏被燒盡\N也不會讓你行前一步的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.42,0:13:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅\N這樣下去空神丸會溶掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我去叫戰神丸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這附近有電話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.13,0:13:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.27,0:13:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶你去吧,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,我們現在來救你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,花開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.61,0:14:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和空神丸一起變燒鳥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.86,0:14:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…復活聖水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.35,0:14:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全靠你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.26,0:14:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得以重生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.86,0:14:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是龍神丸,古拿瑪很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!\N來吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.04,0:15:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,成功了呢,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.00,0:15:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.15,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這混蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再讓你睡多次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.69,0:15:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死!高熱火炎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.13,0:15:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太件事了,森林燒著了\N動物們會燒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒吧!燒吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最討厭大自然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.27,0:16:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏嗎?背叛者!死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.81,0:16:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那愛護一切的心\N還有對抗邪惡的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.25,0:16:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在請再一次\N給我另一個生活力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一個生命?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,和空神丸合體\N便能重生成一部更強的魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名字便是龍王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.13,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍王丸…\N但是空神丸已被燒燬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算身體消失了\N靈魂也仍生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.47,0:16:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是渡\N要我變身成為龍王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有你的愛與勇氣的力量\N是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.98,0:16:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要渡的正義力量完全發放\N我便能變成龍王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.48,0:16:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,大聲呼叫龍王丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.82,0:16:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量全開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.87,0:17:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變身!龍王丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.37,0:17:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸也好,龍王丸也好\N都是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.17,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我令你再次復活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍王丸,用劍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.43,0:18:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.80,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是感動的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.27,0:18:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.57,0:18:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,這是鳳龍冰河劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把火炎…冰封了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.95,0:18:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣只有全身衝上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.62,0:18:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!布力奇2號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!拔劍吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.73,0:18:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.63,0:18:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我記著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸能夠復活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全靠古拿瑪,但是空神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空神丸並沒有死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的靈魂已和龍神丸在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.44,0:19:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!\N鳥先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.35,0:19:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很美的花呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!\N鳥先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.89,0:20:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是古拿瑪原來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.43,0:20:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是很有型的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.23,0:20:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖水的力量\N把多惡達的詛咒解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來的樣子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恢復原來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看,我恢復原來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.67,0:20:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看,黑煙放晴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.20,0:20:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的呢,就好像\N為了古拿瑪而高興一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.16,0:20:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的要走嗎?古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.22,0:21:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這聖水,能令我村內的人\N恢復原來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.46,0:21:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是分離得太突然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.97,0:21:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分離總是來得突然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生要走了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子\N古拿瑪已不是鳥先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.51,0:21:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子 你要保重身體啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.71,0:21:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥兒的樣子比較有型啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.65,0:21:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在的鳥先生\N我也很喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.63,0:21:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,只有一件事\N希望你們答應我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.07,0:21:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要打倒多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.37,0:21:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了,我和你約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.41,0:21:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼也不要說\N有些事用說話是傳達不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.82,0:21:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但心能領會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.55,0:22:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保重了,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.36,0:22:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一路順風!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.66,0:22:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要保重啊!鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.46,0:22:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生,再見!

